  "texts": [
    "However, in the PM-Static scenario, the jets generate a third vortex, labelled V3, which emerges from the top surface.",
    "This corresponds to a peak in the action of the PM-Static controller at this time.",
    "The inability of the PM-Static controller to adapt the amplitude/phase of the input-output behaviour results in suboptimal performance.",
    "Horizon of the finite-history sufficient statisticA parametric study on the horizon of the finite history in the NARX model (2.28), i.e.",
    "the number of frames stacked N fs, is presented in this subsection."
